        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3466431428" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4199150860220773126">I really took my time savoring this book. St. Teresa‚Äôs explication of ‚Äúthe interior castle‚Äù within yourself was definitely described in great detail. I thoroughly enjoyed the book and I‚Äôm glad I took my time reading it. Five stars! </span>

          </span>
